        <!-- This section contains the introduction paragraph -->
        <div class="intro" id="intro">
            <p><em>"Rango"</em> follows the adventures of a chameleon who accidentally ends up in the lawless town of Dirt. Assuming the role of a sheriff, Rango must navigate the challenges of the Wild West, <strong>confront his own identity</strong>, and help the townsfolk save their community from a looming water crisis.</p>
        </div>

